  <brief_title>Study of Plitidepsin (Aplidin®) in Combination With Bortezomib and Dexamethasone in Patients With Multiple Myeloma</brief_title>
  <official_title>Phase I Study of Plitidepsin (Aplidin®) in Combination With Bortezomib and Dexamethasone in Patients With Relapsed and/or Refractory Multiple Myeloma</official_title>
